Raw data processing

Sau-Chin Chen

2020/11/12

{r setup, include=FALSE} knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE)

  1. Export data file (.json) from JATOS server.

  1. Save the data file (.json) in 4_Data.

  1. Transfer the format of data file in OpenSesame.

  1. Make sure the data file format is .csv.

  1. Run read_OS_output.R and retrieve the participant id(s) who complete the study.

  1. Paste the id to Prolific dashboard and export the participants meta data.

  1. Run Rawdata_filter.R and export the valid rawdata for the analysis.
